These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, cola, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, reading, fishing, card-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, house, trance, dubstep
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan dubstep##3
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the fan house##6
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking cola or the person who's hobby is fishing is the fan trance, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking cola and the fan funk have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan trance##3
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the fan dubstep##5
 9. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person drinking lemonade and the fan funk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | cola   | iced-tea      | lemonade    |
| Hobby         | writing     | fishing | reading | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | funk | dubstep         | house     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, pumpkin, potato, tomato
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, malaysian, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, hamster, ferret
 1. the brazilian is the person eating tomato or the owner of the ferret is the brazilian, but not both##10
 2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
 4. the owner of the hamster and the brazilian have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 8. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
 9. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
10. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
11. the nigerian is in an even position##4
12. the brazilian is the person eating watermelon or the brazilian is the owner of the ferret, but not both##10
13. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person eating potato##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | tomato | pumpkin    | watermelon | potato    |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | brazilian | canadian  | nigerian |
| Pet           | hamster     | ferret    | rabbit    | turtle    |

