.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, 7up, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: avocado, lemon, cucumber, peas
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, colombian, dutch
1. the person eating peas is the australian##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
3. the person eating peas is the dutch or the person eating peas is the person drinking soy-milk, but not both##10
4. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
5. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
6. the indonesian is between the person eating avocado and the australian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk         | 7up     | soy-milk | mirinda |
| Food          | avocado | lemon | peas         | cucumber   |
| Nationality   | colombian     | indonesian   | australian       | dutch   |

