.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, strawberry, peas, broccoli
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, camping, magic-tricks, collecting
There are 4 different nationalities: german, malaysian, nigerian, russian
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the malaysian##1
 2. the german is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is not the german##6
 6. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person eating strawberry##5
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the nigerian or the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating strawberry, but not both##10
 8. the nigerian is the person eating peas or the nigerian is the person who's hobby is camping, but not both##10
 9. the russian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person eating peas##7
10. the russian is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | broccoli  | watermelon   | strawberry | peas  |
| Hobby         | filmmaking     | magic-tricks  | camping | collecting |
| Nationality   | german | malaysian | russian  | nigerian |

