.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, fanta, 7up
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, animation, documentary, spy
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, chinchilla, goat
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person watching animation movies##6
 3. the owner of the frog is between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person watching spy movies##6
 5. the owner of the goat and the person watching disaster movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking tea is the person watching disaster movies or the person drinking tea is the owner of the guinea-pig, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 8. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking 7up##7
12. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | tea   | 7up | almond-milk | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | animation    | disaster   | spy |
| Pet           | guinea-pig    | frog | chinchilla    | goat  |

