 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 4. the person driving the boat and the japanese have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the japanese is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 7. the german is on the far right##1
 8. the turkish is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the french##7
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
10. the japanese is between the person driving the tram and the turkish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |
