4 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony, guinea-pig, snake
 1. the person eating mango is not to the left of the person eating pear##8
 2. the dressmaker is between the owner of the rabbit and the person eating mango##2
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the writer##3
 4. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person eating papaya and the owner of the pony##7
 5. the owner of the pony and the person eating pineapple have the same parity positions##9
 6. the mechanic is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the lawyer is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is the dressmaker or the owner of the rabbit is the person eating pear, but not both##10
10. the owner of the rabbit and the mechanic have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3        |     4      |
| Food   | pear    | pineapple     | mango         | papaya |
| Job    | mechanic | dressmaker    | lawyer | writer    |
| Pet    | rabbit      | pony | guinea-pig            | snake   |

