 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating eggplant##5
 9. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's hobby is reading or the person who's hobby is reading is the person eating artichoke, but not both##10
11. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

